'''漿細胞性龜頭炎'''，或稱'''漿細胞性侷限性龜頭炎'''<ref name="pmid7815607">{{cite journal |author=Davis DA, Cohen PR |title=Balanitis circumscripta plasmacellularis |journal=J. Urol. |volume=153 |issue=2 |pages=424–6 |date=February 1995 |pmid=7815607 |doi=10.1097/00005392-199502000-00043 |url=http://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0022-5347(01)67779-6 |access-date=2014-03-21 |archive-date=2019-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191202024652/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0022-5347(01)67779-6 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 是一種發生在男性[[龜頭|龜頭]]上的炎症，是有[[漿細胞|漿細胞]]浸潤特徵的良性皮膚損傷。<ref name="Andrews">{{cite book |author=James, William D.; Berger, Timothy G.; et al. |title=Andrews' Diseases of the Skin: clinical Dermatology |publisher=Saunders Elsevier |location= |year=2006 |pages= |isbn=0-7216-2921-0 |oclc= |doi= |accessdate=}}</ref>{{rp|657}}<ref name="Bolognia">{{cite book |author=Rapini, Ronald P.; Bolognia, Jean L.; Jorizzo, Joseph L. |title=Dermatology: 2-Volume Set |publisher=Mosby |location=St. Louis |year=2007 |pages=Chapter 72 |isbn=1-4160-2999-0 |oclc= |doi= |accessdate=}}</ref>

同樣發生在女性身上則稱為[[外陰炎|外陰炎]]，<ref name="pmid7490049">{{cite journal |author=Neri I, Patrizi A, Marzaduri S, Marini R, Negosanti M |title=Vulvitis plasmacellularis: two new cases |journal=Genitourin Med |volume=71 |issue=5 |pages=311–3 |date=October 1995 |pmid=7490049 |pmc=1195548 |doi= |url=}}</ref> 因為極有誤診的可能，所以其存在與否還有爭議。<ref name="Bolognia" /> 1952年被J·J·Zoon在1962年發現，因此有時也稱Zoon's balanitis、Zoon's erythroplasia、Zoon's vulvitis。<ref name="pmid12979576">{{cite journal |author=Zoon JJ |title=[Chronic benign circumscript plasmocytic balanoposthitis.] |language= |journal=Dermatologica |volume=105 |issue=1 |pages=1–7 |year=1952 |pmid=12979576 |doi= |url=}}</ref>

